<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Volleyball quiz </title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Quiz</h1>

<form>

    <div>
        <p>1. How many players are on the court in one volleyball team?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q1"> 5<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q1"> 6<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q1"> 7<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q1"> 8<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>2. What is the height of the men's volleyball net?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q2"> 2.24 m<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q2"> 2.43 m<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q2"> 2.50 m<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q2"> 2.60 m<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>3. Which country invented volleyball?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q3"> USA<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q3"> India<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q3"> Japan<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q3"> Brazil<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>4. What is the maximum number of touches allowed per team?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q4"> 2<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q4"> 3<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q4"> 4<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q4"> 5<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>5. What is a powerful attacking hit called?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q5"> Serve<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q5"> Spike<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q5"> Pass<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q5"> Block<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>6. What starts a rally in volleyball?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q6"> Pass<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q6"> Serve<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q6"> Set<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q6"> Block<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>7. What is the role of a libero?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q7"> Attacker<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q7"> Defender<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q7"> Server<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q7"> Referee<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>8. How many sets are played in a standard match?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q8"> 3<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q8"> 5<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q8"> 7<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q8"> 9<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>9. Which hit is used to receive the serve?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q9"> Bump<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q9"> Spike<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q9"> Serve<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q9"> Block<br>
    </div>

    <div>
        <p>10. What is it called when the ball lands outside the boundary?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q10"> In<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q10"> Out<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q10"> Fault<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q10"> Net<br>
    </div>

    <br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    <input type="reset" value="Reset">

</form>

</body>
</html>
